<h2 style="color: #333333; margin-bottom: 20px;">Great news! <%= productName %> is back in stock!</h2>

<p>You asked us to notify you when this item became available, and we're happy to let you know it's now back in stock.</p>

<div style="border: 1px solid #eeeeee; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
    <% if (productImage) { %>
    <img src="<%= productImage %>" alt="<%= productName %>" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; object-fit: cover; margin-right: 20px; border-radius: 4px;">
    <% } %>
    <div>
      <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><%= productName %></h3>
      <% if (variantDetails) { %>
      <p style="color: #666666; margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><%= variantDetails %></p>
      <% } %>
      <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">
        $<%= price.toFixed(2) %>
        <% if (previousPrice && previousPrice > price) { %>
        <span style="text-decoration: line-through; color: #999999; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 10px;">
          $<%= previousPrice.toFixed(2) %>
        </span>
        <span style="color: #22c55e; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 10px;">
          <%= Math.round((1 - price / previousPrice) * 100) %>% OFF
        </span>
        <% } %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
  <a href="<%= productUrl %>" class="button">Shop Now</a>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #fee2e2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #dc2626;"><strong>âš¡ Limited Availability</strong><br>
  This item is in high demand. Don't miss out - order soon!</p>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">
  You received this email because you requested to be notified when this product became available. 
  If you no longer wish to receive these notifications, you can <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>" style="color: #666666; text-decoration: underline;">unsubscribe here</a>.
</p>